{"tid":254586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊搞政治領袖文憑課程 學費$28,000","createTime":"2017-05-23T09:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T18:11:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1532d1f35948bf5c6b548abe72e44fc8ab9ff597","tid":254586,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495532467_ad57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495532467_ad57.jpg&h=6bdf11fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主思路籌備一年後，今日宣布成立「香港政治與行政學苑」，將與HKU Space推出為期一年「資深行政人員文憑（政治領袖）」課程，今年十月開學，校長為王于漸。根據學苑資料，已答允出任講者的包括史丹福大學教授陳明銶、林煥光、徐立之、曾鈺成、李彭廣、沈旭輝、盧兆興、黃宏發、陳祖為、宋恩榮、石永泰等。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊表示，希望收取20至35名學生，民主思路會視乎報名人士的質素和需要，決定他們是否需要全數支付28000元的學費，入讀人士亦要附合大學入學要求。湯家驊希望，有足夠決心從政的年輕人可參與報名，希望學員能夠與新一屆政府「有更密切的連繫」。<br />\n<br />\n民主思路代表麥嘉晉表示，民主思路今次不是設立黨校，希望報名人士來自不同政治派別。湯家驊則指，從政人士要有宏觀視野，不能只嗌口號，除政圈中人，亦歡迎公務員、商界、非政府組織人士參與，透露表現優秀的學員，有機會可以向政策官員分享研究成果。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊今日又「封口」拒談是否將加入行會，只笑說自己短期內將去旅行，「宜家唔去幾時再得閒去？」，令在場傳媒都覺得他不言而喻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56731925&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56731925%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=764b338a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56731925%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=9a14acb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56731925&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a>"},{"pid":"d6dd9b57eea4e2db1e7883985ddce9ac38a74da5","tid":254586,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"a0286a33baab33bb51e98964d66dbe51273c2655","tid":254586,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"學做25仔？"},{"pid":"d1c07d8d4a0f32b38e77a5bdffdeff8ca6ba0667","tid":254586,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8903c9ad273b8f830de4a384e36fbfb6586ff64d","tid":254586,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fabd11fb81960886535f553ee6ef3e89b426f410","tid":254586,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"如果想投共不如直接去搵民賤"},{"pid":"173783c09b70f2f7dbbac8466977b902d3f15ec4","tid":254586,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"學衰11？"},{"pid":"31ee5d0ad2d4d29ce0a7bb18c8fd6c39374dfad8","tid":254586,"uid":39898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"普羅d fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4b6b8873ef9829b66175c571314a42753cde82","tid":254586,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:52:09.000Z","msg":"巧立名目cap水啫<br />\n<br />\n你估咩人會報？<br />\n根本係俾錢佢使"},{"pid":"71e3e7540e24e6a97ea86ea41d9f0f537400de9f","tid":254586,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:07:27.000Z","msg":"不如直接入禮義廉仲快上位，仲有津貼添"},{"pid":"0e2f11262b8849cd0283f4535cf761ffb853f921","tid":254586,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:11:56.000Z","msg":"投共洗乜跟你學<br />\n搵賤聯工賊根正紅苗唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}